column5: well the season out here is finally coming to a close...made it out yesterday for the last time...its been a long winter out here but the fishing was good heres a few shots of yesterdays fish...only a wee one, but it was a beauty day on the ice...   gotta love the t-shirt's on the ice     I'll try to post a wrap up of the winters fish later today...has been a long time since I posted a pic and not sure if these are gonna work...lets hope!  Cheers: Brkygetr
Awesome report. I think you get the last guy on the ice award this year.
Some nice stuff !!!! Now bring on open water...
Wow, super fish for this late in the year.  Good going  Joey
